trans-unit.source: The ServiceNameElement class represents a configuration element for a service name used in a <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 有关在中使用的服务名称，ServiceNameElement 类表示一个配置元素<xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref> class.

When this constructor is used to initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement> class, the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A> property is set to `null`.
trans-unit.target: 当使用此构造函数初始化的新实例<xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement>类，<xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A>属性设置为`null`。</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A> </xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A> property should be set to an appropriate value for the application before calling the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection.Add%2A> method to add the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement> instance to the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A>属性应设置为适当的值在调用<xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection.Add%2A>方法将添加<xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement>到<xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection>类</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection>的实例</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement></xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection.Add%2A>之前应用程序</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the Service Provider Name (SPN) for this <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置此服务提供程序名称 (SPN) <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"> </xref>实例。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that contains the representation of SPN for this <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.String>，其中包含的表示形式的 SPN 这<xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref>实例。</xref:System.String>
